title: Honky Tonk Freeway
description: Hoping to lure tourist bucks ,a tiny Florida town tries and fails to get an off ramp on a major highway and takes matters into its own hands ... with dynamite. Huge cast with notables like Jessica Tandy and Hume Cronyn and Geraldine Page co-star with other names of the period in English director John Schlesinger's acid ode to greed and the open road. Little seen because it was pulled from release after it opened. Reseeded on request.
